Interface Unmarshaller

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractElementExtensibleXMLObjectUnmarshaller, AbstractExtensibleXMLObjectUnmarshaller, AbstractXMLObjectUnmarshaller, BaseXMLObjectUnmarshaller, XSAnyUnmarshaller, XSBase64BinaryUnmarshaller, XSBooleanUnmarshaller, XSDateTimeUnmarshaller, XSIntegerUnmarshaller, XSQNameUnmarshaller, XSStringUnmarshaller, XSURIUnmarshaller

    public interface Unmarshaller
    Unmarshallers are used to unmarshall a W3C DOM element into a XMLObject.
